Name: CFG-CV00014476
LLC_BI__Description__c: This value controls which fields should not clone when you do a renewal or modification. The value should be the field set which includes the fields you do not want cloned.

Name: CFG-CV00014477
LLC_BI__Description__c: This specifies what the status a renewed or modified loan is placed in.

Name: CFG-CV00014478
LLC_BI__Description__c: This specifies what the stage a renewed or modified loan is placed in.

Name: CFG-CV00014479
LLC_BI__Description__c: This specifies what related lists should clone immediately when you renew or modify the loan.

Name: CFG-CV00014480
LLC_BI__Description__c: This specifies what related lists should clone asynchronously when you renew or modify the loan.

Name: CFG-CV00014481
LLC_BI__Description__c: You should specify true in the value field to specify the Budget should clone. It always performs asynchronously.

Name: CFG-CV00014482
LLC_BI__Description__c: You should specify true in the value field to specify the Rate and Payment Structure should clone. It always performs asynchronously.

Name: CFG-CV00014483
LLC_BI__Description__c: You should specify true in the value field to specify the Credit Memo should clone. It always performs asynchronously.

Name: CFG-CV00014484
LLC_BI__Description__c: This Configuration will specify what stage a loan must be in before a specific credit action can be performed on it

Name: CFG-CV00014485
LLC_BI__Description__c: This Configuration will specify what status a loan must be in before a specific credit action can be performed on it

Name: CFG-CV00014486
LLC_BI__Description__c: The value appended to the loan number for loans in process of renewal or modification. To update this appendage, update the fieldValue. The Product Type cannot override the value.

Name: CFG-CV00014487
LLC_BI__Description__c: The value appended to the loan number for loans in process of renewal or modification. To update this appendage, update the fieldValue. The Product Type cannot override the value.
